	<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年，市经信委深入贯彻党的十九大精神，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-bidi-font-size: 12.0pt">坚持“服务企业就是服务经济”理念，全力提升“经信惠企”品牌影响力，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">以新修订的《中小企业促进法》为指引，重点搭建融资担保、人才培训等中小企业公共服务平台，创新服务手段，拓展服务内容，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-font-kerning: 0pt">提升效率效能，</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">全力打造</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">经信惠企</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">服务品牌，促进中小企业实现转型升级可持续发展。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><?xml:namespace prefix = o ns = "urn:schemas-microsoft-com:office:office" /><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 31.5pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly" class=MsoNormal><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">一是完善融资担保体系。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">做大国有担保，推进高新创业担保等</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>3</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家国有担保公司业务稳定发展；落实担保政策，为中小企业提供低费率担保，市级财政给予扶持</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>498</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万元。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年末，全市担保余额</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>15</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元。</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">二是做好转贷资金管理</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">修订资金管理办法，降低企业门槛，提高使用额度，增加合作银行数量，建设网上申报平台，共同推进转贷业务增长。全年累计为</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>98</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家企业提供转贷应急资金</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>8.9</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元，降低企业融资成本</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1365</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万元。</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">三是加强企业人才培训</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">制定培训管理办法，区别企业家和中层管理人员培训对象，实施双品牌运作。昆山经信企业家学院举办</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>9</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">期，培训</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>430</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">人次；昆山经信企业大讲堂举办</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>79</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">场，培训人数超</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>5700</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">人次。</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">四是实施企业信用贯标</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">印发贯标工作方案，实行一对一服务，精心组织现场验收。全年完成信用贯标</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>60</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家，创建苏州市级示范企业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家，省级示范企业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家。</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">五是推进科技小巨人培育</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">鼓励企业专注细分市场，打造中小企业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>“</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">隐形冠军</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>”</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">发展梯队，培育一批专精特新中小企业。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2017</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年培育企业增至</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>226</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家，实现销售收入</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>643</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元，其中超亿元</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>150</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家，超</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>10</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元企业</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>5</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家，新增</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>8</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家进入全国细分市场前十位。</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">六是加大小微企业扶持</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">组织小微工业企业投入项目申报，共有</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>55</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">个项目获扶持资金</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1023</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万元，拉动企业投资</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1.1</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">亿元。项目集中在精密机械和电子信息两大主导产业，主要购置加工中心、自动化设备等智能装备，企业呈现速度和效益双增长的良好发展态势。</SPAN><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 楷体_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">七是鼓励企业技术创新</SPAN></B><B style="mso-bidi-font-weight: normal"><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">。</SPAN></B><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">积极向上争取，立讯精密等</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">家企业获省专精特新产品认定，萨驰华辰获省科技小巨人认定，联滔电子获省管理创新示范企业称号，亿科检测获省中小企业公共技术服务平台荣誉。实施中小企业信息化券，发放</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>185</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">张服务券，扶持金额</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>500</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万元，带动企业信息化投入</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>1013</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">万元。</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US><o:p></o:p></SPAN></P>
<P style="TEXT-ALIGN: left; LINE-HEIGHT: 30pt; TEXT-INDENT: 32pt; MARGIN: 0cm 0cm 0pt; mso-line-height-rule: exactly; mso-pagination: widow-orphan; mso-char-indent-count: 2.0" class=MsoNormal align=left><SPAN style="FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-fareast-font-family: 仿宋_GB2312" lang=EN-US>2018</SPAN><SPAN style="FONT-FAMILY: 仿宋_GB2312; FONT-SIZE: 16pt; mso-ascii-font-family: ''Times New Roman''">年，经信委将聚焦中小企业服务，找准目标、定好靶向，<SPAN style="COLOR: black">不忘初心优服务、深耕细作惠万企，在优质服务上着力、在主动服务上下劲、在高效服务上用功、在精准服务上突破，服务企业</SPAN>工作更加务实，中小企业扶持更加精准，工业企业发展更加稳健。</SPAN></P>
